<P>Priore&s;ies. Dna Cri&s;tiana oc. ad pentec. 1233&mdash;Sibil Gategang 1331. Dna Alice Davill 9 May, 1355&mdash;Ami&s;ia de Belford 10 Jun. 1367&mdash;Katerina 21 Sep. 1403 (Rot Skirlaw Bp No. 93).&mdash;Margaret Hawke&s;well, 1 May, 1446 (Madox form. p. 271.)&mdash;Agnes Danby, 9 Oct. 1471.&mdash;Johanna Baxter, 20 Aug. 1486. Dame Joan Pr. granted a lea&s;e 4 King Hen. VII. A. D. 1486. Johanna. She re&s;igned for a pen&s;ion of 1l. 10s. per ann.&mdash;Agnes Law&s;on la&s;t Priore&s;s. She &s;urrendered this Convent 3 Jan. 1540, 31 King Hen. VIII. before Ric. Layton, one, &amp;c. and had a pen&s;ion of 6l. per ann. a&s;&s;igned her, which &s;he enjoyed in 1553, in which year remained in charge the following pen&s;ions.&mdash;Johanna Priore&s;s 1l. 10l. Johanna Brodrigge 1l. 6s. 8d. Johanna Younger 1l. 6s. 8d. Eliz. Cranmer 1l. 6s. 8d. and to Cecily Middleton 1l. 6s. 8d.</P>
