<P>Ma&s;ters.&mdash;John de Bland 1374. 15 Feb. 1569, the Mayor and Burge&s;&s;es of Newca&s;tle granted the next pre&s;entation of St M. Magdalen, called the Maidlenes, to Hen Ander&s;on, Rob. Mit|ford, and Chr. Mitford.&mdash;Edm. Wy&s;eman, in&s;t. 5 Oct. 1564. This took no effect. &mdash; Rob. Mydforde 1586.
