<L>And mo&s;t de&s;tructive vices,</L>
<L>May reign and &s;pread with triumphant havock,</L>
<L>Under the mild connivance, mi&s;taken confidence, and unmerited favour</L>
<L>Of a mo&s;t gracious and virtuous &s;overeign;</L>
